<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal"><font style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">Hi {!Lead.FirstName},<br></span><br>Thanks for getting in touch via&nbsp;<b>On the Tools</b>.<br><br>My name is&nbsp;{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;and I’ll be giving you a call to run through your business insurance needs.&nbsp;<br><br>So, you know when to expect my call - our office is open between the hours of 8:00am-5:30pm, Monday-Friday.&nbsp;<b>Need me to call at a specific time?</b>&nbsp;<b><a href="https://calendly.com/d/crv2-4cb-zcj/kingsbridge-insurance-call-back-on-the-tools">Book a call slot</a>.<br><br></b></font><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Not able to answer calls during the day?</span></b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Send me a message on WhatsApp using&nbsp;<b><a href="https://go.kingsbridge.co.uk/ott-ar-whatsapp">07917 515428</a></b>&nbsp;and I’ll contact you via message instead.<br></span><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br>Alternatively, contact me on&nbsp;<b>01242 808 740</b>. Our office is open 8:00am-5:30pm, Monday-Friday.&nbsp;<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>I look forward to catching up with you soon!<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Thanks,<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><font style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</font></p>]]></td>
</tr>
